#Lyrics
[Tone 1] The Lord is my shepherd; I shall not want. (Psalm 23:1) [Tone 2] Make haste, O God, to deliver me! (Psalm 70:1) [Tone 3] I was glad when they said to me, "Let us go to the house of the Lord!" (Psalm 122:1) [Tone 4] The Lord is my light and my salvation; whom shall I fear? (Psalm 27:1) [Tone 5] O Lord, open my lips, and my mouth will declare your praise. (Psalm 51:15) [Tone 6] Blessed is the one whose transgression is forgiven. (Psalm 32:1) [Tone 7] The Lord is my strength and my shield. (Psalm 28:7) [Tone 8] Oh come, let us sing to the Lord. (Psalm 95:1)

